data.text:
Is the registration of your firm, foundation, organization or association already subject for revocation by the Securities and Exchange Commission? Because you have not made a yearly report for at least five years since 2007.

Below are the SEC-registered firms/entities whose registrations are deemed revoked (but you still have a remedy to make amends with the SEC. Find out the ways by visiting http://cha4t.wordpress.com):

Note: the list is alphabetical but for easier search, just make CONTROL + F in your keyboard and type the name of your firm/entity/organization.

Final list of 2007 registered corporations for revocation of Certificate of Incorporation:

* Note: the first entry above the name of entity is your entity’s SEC Registration Number. There are 10,055 of them.
